## PR Workflow

### Pre-PR Check

```bash
git fetch origin main && \
git log --oneline origin/main..HEAD && \
git diff --stat origin/main..HEAD
```

### Create PR

```bash
gh pr create --title "type(scope): description" --body "## Summary
- [bullet points]

## Test Plan
- [testing steps]"
```

